abstract: Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, Iran's supreme leader, warns nation to be on guard against attempts by United States to infiltrate society in effort to change individual beliefs and undermine Iranian solidarity.
lead_paragraph: Iran’s top leader warned Wednesday the United States is using “money and sexual attractions” and to not fall into the “enemy’s trap.”

headline.main: Ayatollah Ali Khamenei Says U.S. Using Money and Sex to Infiltrate Iran
